      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Will She Hear Them</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>My life are spinning round with my emotions </l>
          <l>will i tell her how i feel? </l>
          <l>Will she reject me or except me </l>
          <l>i don't know but i have to figure out </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>My life are passing by with my creation </l>
          <l>i'm picturing her in my mind </l>
          <l>There she's my lover my lust and desire </l>
          <l>see the fire in her eyes </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>But hopes they are remaining like a secret </l>
          <l>will she hear them when i'm passing by </l>
          <l>and when can i find courage in my eyes </l>
          <l>Will i ever speak loud</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
